**NearMe15** is a prototype **Streamlit application** developed during the **Snowflake x Catalyst Public Service Hackathon** in Edinburgh on **11 June 2025**.

The app helps users assess how "15-minute" their city isâ€”i.e., how many essential services are reachable within a short distance of a given postcode.

